Package: loopcityData
Title: Experimental Data for the loopcity Package
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("Sarah", "Parker", role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "smp3800@gmail.com",
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2700-3979"))
Description: Provides Hi-C loop calls and processed chromatin interaction data
    used in examples and vignettes for the loopcity package. Small datasets
    (GM12878 10 kb loop calls) are shipped directly; larger files (K562 Hi-C
    contact matrices, CTCF and H3K27ac ChIP-seq signal tracks) are accessed
    on demand via ExperimentHub.
License: CC BY 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0),
    ExperimentHub
Imports:
    AnnotationHub,
    InteractionSet
Suggests:
    loopcity,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    BiocStyle
VignetteBuilder: knitr
biocViews: ExperimentHub, ExperimentData, Homo_sapiens_Data,
    HighThroughputSequencing, HiC, ChIPSeq
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
BugReports: https://github.com/sarmapar/loopcity/issues
URL: https://github.com/sarmapar/loopcity
